    "description": "Angus and the Gates of Chaos tells the story of Angus, the half-witted son of a tax collector in the fictional universe of Chanceburn. Through a series of coincidences, Angus finds himself on a quest to defeat the evil Inquisitor Ruthen and prevent him from opening the Gates of Chaos and destroying all of Chanceburn.<br><br>Enjoy a classic, retro style adventure featuring ice puzzles, hidden collectibles, three endings, varied difficulty modes, and jokes about taxes. Lots of jokes about taxes. Proceed with caution.<br><br><br><strong>ABOUT DIFFICULTY MODES</strong><br>Easy - Enjoy the game's story and solve some puzzles! Minimal Challenge.<br>Normal - Dodge obstacles and solve puzzles at the same time! The Intended Game Experience.<br>Hard - Game too easy? Good luck beating this mode. For those who want a brutally hard challenge.",
